&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt;  ☞&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4NTY3OTU3MA==&amp;amp;mid=2247484090&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=c4778f29071d0388f6f7d5d25b2207d3&amp;amp;chksm=ebe9c807dc9e4111784b02ad43ed7b9958a0da5108c9db84a659f2b1d853a4a982bcef72aacc&amp;amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-itemshowtype=&quot;0&quot; data-linktype=&quot;2&quot;&gt;线性相关和秩的物理意义&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
